    "introduction": "Cat Ce is a comedian, actress, model, and filmmaker. She fell in love with the performing arts at a young age when she studied dance, music, and martial arts. She produces and headlines her own stand-up comedy shows at The Ice House in Pasadena, California. Cat Ce started touring in 2024 and headlining her shows at Jimmy Kimmel’s Comedy Club, Irvine Improv, Brea Improv, Cap City Comedy Club, Helium Comedy Club and numerous other comedy venues.Cat has also produced and starred in other acclaimed comedy shows such as Crazy Funny Asians and charity shows for Children’s Miracle Network Hospitals.In addition, she has been part of numerous film, television, video shoots and photo shoots. Cat is a strong supporter of various animal welfare and environmental groups and has devoted her spare time by volunteering at animal shelters.",
